28/01/2010
ATHENS, Greece -- Alternate Foreign Minister Dimitris Droutsas said Wednesday (January 27th) that a set-back on delineating its maritime border with Albania in the Ioanian Sea requires an explanation from Tirana. On Tuesday, Albanian media reported that the Constitutional Court would strike down the April 2009 agreement and require its renegotiation. (BBC, Ora News, Shekulli, Top Channel, Balkan Web - 27/01/10)
